        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="mBlock"><a href="#mBlock" class="headerlink" title="mBlock"></a>mBlock</h2><p>是使用Scratch2.0進而開發出的圖形化編輯軟體，mBlock支援Arduino的程式編輯，<br>可以輕鬆讓小朋友學習程式。</p><a id="more"></a><h3 id="mblock安裝"><a href="#mblock安裝" class="headerlink" title="mblock安裝"></a>mblock安裝</h3><p><a href="http://learn.makeblock.com/cn/software/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">mblock官方網頁</a><br>選擇對應的電腦作業系統版本<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/QEoOdbc.png" alt="圖一"><br>接下來會分三個版本</p><ul><li>網頁</li><li>桌面</li><li>APP<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/34e4rXD.png" alt="圖二"></li></ul><p>我個人是安裝桌面版本<br>打開安裝檔<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/XUS5pau.png" alt="圖三"><br>再來就是一直下一步就OK囉~<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/AMY4NDZ.png" alt="圖四"><br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/55BFgh7.jpg" alt="圖五"><br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/TPJb90q.jpg" alt="圖六"><br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/OH4sNb9.jpg" alt="圖七"><br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/T6qmVUU.jpg" alt="圖八"><br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/6tAZ9RC.jpg" alt="圖九"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
